<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN"><head><meta charset="UTF-8"><style>
  :root { --accent: #fbbf24; --teal: #5eead4; --pink: #fb7185;
    --A: #60a5fa; --B: #34d399; --E: #fb923c; --F: #c084fc; }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
  html, body { width: 1200px; height: 675px; overflow: hidden;
    font-family: -apple-system, "PingFang SC", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei", "Inter", "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
    color: #fff;
    background:
      radial-gradient(800px 500px at 50% -10%, rgba(94,234,212,0.18), transparent 60%),
      linear-gradient(180deg, #0a0f1e 0%, #07091a 100%);
  }
  .frame { padding: 44px 56px; height: 100%; display: flex; flex-direction: column; }
  .title { font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 4px; color: var(--accent); font-weight: 800; }
  h2 { font-size: 46px; line-height: 1.22; font-weight: 900; margin: 8px 0 6px; letter-spacing: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #c2c9dc);
    -webkit-background-clip: text; background-clip: text; -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }
  .sub { font-size: 20px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65); margin-bottom: 24px; font-weight: 600; }

  .container { flex: 1; display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.3fr; gap: 30px; }

  .left { display: flex; flex-direction: column; align-items: center; gap: 10px; }
  .lead-box {
    padding: 14px 22px; border: 2px solid var(--accent);
    background: rgba(251,191,36,0.12);
    border-radius: 14px; font-weight: 800; font-size: 16px; color: var(--accent);
    text-align: center;
  }
  .lead-box .lbl { display: block; font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 3px; opacity: 0.8; margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .fanout { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.3); font-size: 13px; letter-spacing: 4px; margin: 3px 0; }
  .agents { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); gap: 7px; width: 100%; }
  .agent {
    padding: 8px 4px; border-radius: 8px; text-align: center;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.12);
    font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 1.25;
  }
  .agent .nm { font-size: 14px; color: var(--accent); }
  .agent.A { border-color: rgba(96,165,250,0.4); }
  .agent.A .nm { color: var(--A); }
  .agent.B { border-color: rgba(52,211,153,0.4); }
  .agent.B .nm { color: var(--B); }
  .agent.E { border-color: rgba(251,146,60,0.4); }
  .agent.E .nm { color: var(--E); }
  .agent.F { border-color: rgba(192,132,252,0.4); }
  .agent.F .nm { color: var(--F); }

  .timing {
    text-align: center; padding: 10px 12px; margin-top: 10px;
    background: rgba(94,234,212,0.08); border: 1px solid rgba(94,234,212,0.3);
    border-radius: 10px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.4;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .timing .lbl { font-size: 10px; letter-spacing: 3px; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .timing s { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45); text-decoration-color: var(--pink); }
  .timing b { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 900; }

  .dims {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03); border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);
    border-radius: 14px; padding: 18px 22px;
    display: flex; flex-direction: column;
  }
  .dims h3 {
    font-size: 14px; color: var(--accent); margin-bottom: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 2px; font-weight: 800;
  }
  .dim-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 8px 18px; }
  .dim { display: flex; gap: 8px; align-items: baseline; font-size: 12px; }
  .dim .ix { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 900; font-size: 12px; min-width: 14px; }
  .dim .lbl { color: #e8ecf5; font-weight: 700; }
  .dim .desc { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.55); font-size: 11px; }
  .dims-foot {
    margin-top: auto; padding-top: 10px; border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
    font-size: 11.5px; color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .dims-foot b { color: var(--pink); font-weight: 800; }
</style></head>
<body>
<div class="frame">
  <div class="title">核心机制 · 一条消息 FAN-OUT</div>
  <h2>一条消息派 7 个 sub-agent<br><span style="color:var(--teal)">= 30 分钟，不是 28 小时</span></h2>
  <div class="sub">每个 agent 领 ~8 个项目，跑 8 维度 DD，回 JSON。</div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="left">
      <div class="lead-box"><span class="lbl">领头 AGENT</span>Claude（你）</div>
      <div class="fanout">↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓ ↓</div>
      <div class="agents">
        <div class="agent A"><div class="nm">A</div><div>前沿</div></div>
        <div class="agent B"><div class="nm">B1</div><div>具身</div></div>
        <div class="agent B"><div class="nm">B2</div><div>具身</div></div>
        <div class="agent E"><div class="nm">E1</div><div>Agent toB</div></div>
        <div class="agent E"><div class="nm">E2</div><div>Agent toB</div></div>
        <div class="agent F"><div class="nm">F1</div><div>Agent toC</div></div>
        <div class="agent F"><div class="nm">F2</div><div>Agent toC</div></div>
        <div class="agent" style="opacity:0.4;"><div class="nm">—</div><div>备用</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="timing">
        <div class="lbl">串行 VS 并行</div>
        <s>28 小时</s> &nbsp;→&nbsp; <b>30 分钟</b>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="dims">
      <h3>8 维度 DD（每项目）</h3>
      <div class="dim-grid">
        <div class="dim"><span class="ix">1</span><div><div class="lbl">站点状态</div><div class="desc">curl 状态码 + 重定向</div></div></div>
        <div class="dim"><span class="ix">2</span><div><div class="lbl">仓库活跃度</div><div class="desc">GH API stars / pushed_at</div></div></div>
        <div class="dim"><span class="ix">3</span><div><div class="lbl">团队评分 1-5</div><div class="desc">学历 + 前雇主</div></div></div>
        <div class="dim"><span class="ix">4</span><div><div class="lbl">技术护城河</div><div class="desc">≤ 40 字概括</div></div></div>
        <div class="dim"><span class="ix">5</span><div><div class="lbl">竞品 3-5</div><div class="desc">名称 + 阶段 + 备注</div></div></div>
        <div class="dim"><span class="ix">6</span><div><div class="lbl">市场 TAM</div><div class="desc">TAM + CAGR 一句话</div></div></div>
        <div class="dim"><span class="ix">7</span><div><div class="lbl">估值区间</div><div class="desc">pre-money + 对标</div></div></div>
        <div class="dim"><span class="ix">8</span><div><div class="lbl">风险/优势/推荐度</div><div class="desc">3+3 + 推荐 1-5</div></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="dims-foot">
        ⚠ 铁律：<b>不捏造</b>创始人姓名 / 融资金额。<br>
        注入 25 赛道估值对标表 —— agent 不在真空里报价。
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</body></html>
